Package ie.gmit.sw

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    Alpha
    This is the class object that stores the respective metrics for the class (i.e name, package, interfaces).
    AlphaDB
    This class manages the MicroStream DB for storing class details.
    AlphaFactory
    CustomerFactory is a singleton factory that creates a model (in this case it is hard-wired as a set of Alpha objects) that is returned by the factory method.
    AlphaTableView
    This class was abstracted to encapsulate the getTabeView method.
    AppWindow
    This class brings all of the separated class components together, and implements them into a stage, which contains the tableview, file chooser pane, a toolbar which contains multiple buttons for running queries, and text box for displaying query output.
    FileChoice
    This class encapsulates the File Chooser Pane, which is used for uploading the jar file.
    ProcessFile
    This class processes the jar file inputed by the user.
    Runner
    Runner class for the application, launches the JavaFX application GUI.
